948
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:12,720
 je manja stopa ponavljanja kriminala.

949
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,760
 Tako da, aha, opet govorimo

950
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:15,640
 o unutranjim svijetu.

951
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,580
 Tako da, kužim da tu, ok,

952
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:19,100
 trebaju postojati neke kazne

953
00:31:19,100 --> 00:31:22,080
 za promet i slično i kriminal,

954
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:24,920
 ali djeca se tek razvijaju.

955
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:27,380
 Imaju nas odrasle da im pomažemo,

956
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:28,560
 da ih navigiramo,

957
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:29,800
 jer oni tek uče.

958
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:31,960
 Znači, oni uče osjetiti

959
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:34,820
 koja je to emocija ili potreba,

960
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:36,800
 zbog koje se ponaša na određen način,

961
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:40,060
 učini taj razmag i odabrat bolji put.

962
00:31:41,380 --> 00:31:43,120
 Zašto kazne nemaju smisla?

963
00:31:43,120 --> 00:31:45,120
 Zato što kazne dokazano utječu

964
00:31:45,120 --> 00:31:47,320
 na djetstvu sliku o sebi.

965
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:51,100
 Znači, jer djete stvara sliku o sebi

966
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:54,160
 onakvu kakvu mu ti zrcališ.

967
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,880
 Znači, ako kad se on ponaša loše,

968
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,920
 ti ga pošalješ u sobu,

969
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:01,280
 znači ti si mu zrcalio takav

970
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:02,740
 ne želim da postojiš.

971
00:32:02,740 --> 00:32:05,600
 Znači, ignoriranje je zapravo

972
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:08,780
 pa jednaka kao i fizičko kažnjavanje.

973
00:32:08,780 --> 00:32:10,060
 Znači, zatvaranje u sobu

974
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:12,480
 ili ignoriranje, sad ne pričam s tobom,

975
00:32:12,480 --> 00:32:14,540
 je poruka nemoj postojati.

976
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:15,920
 Neki su čak govorili

977
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:17,200
 iz perspektive djece

978
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,500
 koja je su kažnjavana,

979
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:20,880
 da je bi im teže nekad padalo

980
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:23,020
 ignoriranje i zanemarivanje

981
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:23,920
 nego udarati.

982
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,320
 Jer tu dobijem bar neku pažnju.

983
00:32:25,320 --> 00:32:26,400
 Tu je kontakt neki.

984
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:29,080
 I kad pitaš da li ima korici,

985
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:30,780
 ja sam jednom ili dva put

986
00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:33,260
 na story pitala odrasle osobe

987
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:34,000
 koje me prate.

988
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:37,580
 Što mislite o kazni koju ste dobivali?

989
00:32:37,580 --> 00:32:39,400
 Kako je utjecala na vas

990
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:40,760
 i šta mislite o tome?

991
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:43,080
 Znači, plakala sam dok sam čitala.

992
00:32:43,260 --> 00:32:44,700
 koliko je danas,

993
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,380
 uglavnom su to žene,

994
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:48,380
 jer me prate uglavnom mame,

995
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:50,340
 koliko je boli u tim ženama

996
00:32:50,340 --> 00:32:51,780
 i kad su one meni pisale,

997
00:32:51,780 --> 00:32:52,940
 kako su se osjećale,

998
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:54,200
 to je horor.

999
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:57,380
 Usamljeno, bezvrijedno,

1000
00:32:57,380 --> 00:33:00,240
 konitko i ništa.

1001
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:03,420
 Znači, samo sam se htjela osvetit.

1002
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:07,100
 Razmišljala sam kako ću drugi put sakrit.

1003
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:10,780
 Znači, nijedne nije pisala

1004
00:33:10,780 --> 00:33:13,160
 to je to, naučila sam.

1005
00:33:13,260 --> 00:33:16,280
 Iako ima ljudi koji će na ovaj podcast napisat,

1006
00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:18,700
 tukli su me i treba da jesu,

1007
00:33:18,700 --> 00:33:20,600
 ali ta osoba je toliko odustala od sebe

1008
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:22,140
 da ona smatra da to zavrijeđuje.

1009
00:33:22,820 --> 00:33:25,540
 Jedino kad generalno kažu što nama fali danas,

1010
00:33:25,540 --> 00:33:29,080
 jer pogotovo malo generacije još starije od mene,

1011
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:31,880
 nas su tukli i što nam fali danas,

1012
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,320
 mi smo generalno kao ok.

1013
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:34,680
 Da, ali znaš zašto je to?

1014
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,460
 Ismaš ok.

1015
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,700
 Da, jer kad smo djeca,

1016
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:40,080
 mi roditelje smatramo savršenima.

1017
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:41,900
 I kad nas roditelj kazni,

1018
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:43,220
 mi ne mislimo da je on loš,

1019
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:45,480
 nego uvijek ćemo misliti da smo mi loši.

1020
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:47,900
 Jer ako mislimo da je on loš,

1021
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:48,980
 ko će nas čuvat?

1022
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:51,120
 Mi trebamo tu figuru,

1023
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:52,840
 koja je idealna za nas.

1024
00:33:53,700 --> 00:33:56,480
 I teško je i danas razbiti tu iluziju

1025
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:58,880
 da ti je nešto u djetinstvu nije bilo dobro.

1026
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:01,560
 Djetinstvo je neki naš temelj,

1027
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:04,720
 ono da želiš sad to kopati još po tome

1028
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,820
 da nešto nije bilo u redu,

1029
00:34:05,820 --> 00:34:06,980
 da je nešto moglo bolje.

1030
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,400
 Pogotovo imam osjećaj,

1031
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:11,160
 znam, svjesna sam da i naši roditelji,

1032
00:34:11,160 --> 00:34:12,800
 moram reći,

1033
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:15,040
 moji su stvarno radili po Montessorju,

1034
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:16,440
 a da nisu bili toga ni svjesni

1035
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:18,100
 i blagoslovljena sam s time,

1036
00:34:18,100 --> 00:34:20,100
 ali znam da je bilo roditelja koji

1037
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:21,960
 davali su sve,

1038
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:23,400
 ali samo materialno,

1039
00:34:23,660 --> 00:34:25,140
 i onda ti me misle davali smo sve.

1040
00:34:25,140 --> 00:34:28,380
 I nekako su utkali u svoju djecu

1041
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,460
 sve smo vam dali,

1042
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,020
 sve smo vam dali,

1043
00:34:30,020 --> 00:34:31,680
 možda makar nije bilo pažnje,

1044
00:34:31,680 --> 00:34:33,000
 nije bilo bliskosti,

1045
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,920
 nije bilo masu toga,

1046
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,940
 ali je mantra bila

1047
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:37,180
 sve smo vam dali.

1048
00:34:37,180 --> 00:34:39,080
 I onda je teško spoznat,

1049
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:40,620
 ok, niste mi baš sve dali

1050
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:42,000
 i priznati sebi

1051
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,920
 i onda vučemo to kao

1052
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,380
 sve nam,

1053
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,780
 dobro nam je, ništa nam ne fali,

1054
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:46,540
 ništa nam ne fali,

1055
00:34:46,540 --> 00:34:48,020
 a zapravo ispod toga...

1056
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:49,860
 I onda ponavljamo to sa svojim djecom.

1057
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:50,580
 Da, da.

1058
00:34:50,700 --> 00:34:52,100
 Ali dobro, i sa tim rojiteljima

1059
00:34:52,100 --> 00:34:53,860
 netko nije bio s njihovim emocijama.

1060
00:34:53,860 --> 00:34:54,360
 Emo.

1061
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:55,640
 Naše emocije smo mi.

1062
00:34:55,640 --> 00:34:57,100
 To je naša srž.

1063
00:34:57,100 --> 00:34:59,140
 Znači, naš unutarnji svijet

1064
00:34:59,140 --> 00:35:00,120
 su naše emocije.

1065
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:01,640
 I zapravo ako se ne bave

1066
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:02,840
 rojitelje emocijama,

1067
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,760
 a uglavnom se odgoju ne bave,

1068
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:08,100
 onda zapravo ne baviš se sa mnom.

1069
00:35:08,100 --> 00:35:09,440
 Da, tako da,

1070
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:11,640
 u konečnici

1071
00:35:11,640 --> 00:35:13,360
 kazna ne dovodi.

1072
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,780
 Kažem, može,

1073
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:16,260
 ako jako dobro kaznimo djete,

1074
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:17,920
 ono hoće

1075
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,620
 ne više dirati u čašu

1076
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:21,100
 ili zakasniti iz izlaska,

1077
00:35:21,100 --> 00:35:22,100
 ali

1078
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:24,260
 to jedno kažnjeno djete

1079
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:26,120
 će jako brzo početi vraćati.

1080
00:35:26,120 --> 00:35:26,620
 Na primjer,

1081
00:35:26,620 --> 00:35:28,180
 djete koje je

1082
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:30,080
 kažnjavano često

1083
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:32,400
 i odgajano na taj način,

1084
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,600
 će sutra doć van

1085
00:35:33,600 --> 00:35:34,980
 i zapući će marihuanu

1086
00:35:34,980 --> 00:35:36,040
 samo zato

1087
00:35:36,040 --> 00:35:38,100
 da ima svoje ja.

1088
00:35:38,100 --> 00:35:39,920
 Jer si ga ti kažnjavao.

1089
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,080
 Znači,

1090
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:43,160
 kužiš koliko daleko to ide.

1091
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:44,820
 Isto tako danas ga kažnjavaš,

1092
00:35:44,820 --> 00:35:45,680
 a šta ćeš sutra?

1093
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:47,700
 Znači, sutra

1094
00:35:47,700 --> 00:35:49,400
 imaš, ono,

1095
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,560
 i rojitelji mi pišu,

1096
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:52,160
 on ima sad 15 godina,

1097
00:35:52,160 --> 00:35:52,560
 ja fizički,

1098
00:35:52,560 --> 00:35:55,000
 šta mu ja mogu s njim?

1099
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,700
 I sad mu treba uzeti mobitel,

1100
00:35:56,700 --> 00:35:57,960
 ali opet ne ide.

1101
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,060
 On nađe drugi mobitel.

1102
00:35:59,060 --> 00:36:00,620
 On ode opet van s društvom

1103
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:02,380
 i ti više nemaš kontrolu.

1104
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:03,700
 Dakle, stvar je

1105
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:06,100
 koliko si ti poštovanje

1106
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:08,340
 međusobno sagradio do tad.

1107
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:10,740
 Jer ja želim u životu

1108
00:36:10,740 --> 00:36:12,280
 da me djete sluša

1109
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,260
 jer me poštuje,

1110
00:36:13,260 --> 00:36:14,340
 a ne zato

1111
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,840
 jer me se boji.

1112
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,560
 Da, da.

1113
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:17,360
 Jer kad izađe van,

1114
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,320
 više me se ne boji.

1115
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,760
 Ja ne znam šta on radi.

1116
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:20,820
 Tako da...

1117
00:36:20,820 --> 00:36:22,420
 Mislim, puno je toga toliko

1118
00:36:22,420 --> 00:36:24,480
 zvuči lagano,

1119
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,540
 a u praksi,

1120
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:26,860
 ne znam,

1121
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:28,000
 još mi imamo malu djecu

1122
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,520
 i djećemo kad dođu u pubertet,

1123
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:31,140
 ali sad se to gradi,

1124
00:36:31,140 --> 00:36:32,060
 sad se gradi taj odnos.

1125
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:33,360
 A reci mi,

1126
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:35,500
 da, znači kazne

1127
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:37,220
 općenito ne.

1128
00:36:37,220 --> 00:36:39,760
 Ispomenula si o oduzimanje privilegija.

1129
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:40,400
 Eto.

1130
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,860
 To je isto neka vrsta kazne?

1131
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:43,700
 Je.

1132
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:46,220
 Samo što neki ljudi,

1133
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:49,020
 ne znam koliko su stručni u tome što rade,

1134
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:51,180
 je zagovaraju baš oduzimanje privilegija

1135
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:53,840
 i ja razumijem da je roditeljima to najlakše.

1136
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:54,680
 To je najlakše.

1137
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:57,740
 Znači sve ovo svjesno što sam ti dan bez ekrana,

1138
00:36:57,740 --> 00:36:58,660
 to spada tu kao.

1139
00:36:58,660 --> 00:37:01,420
 Da, da, da, ili nemašeš na rođen da ne uzmem ti mobiteli slično,

1140
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:03,440
 ali ponovno reakcija djeteta je ista.

1141
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:06,100
 Znači želiti se osveti, stvara lošu sliku o sebi,

1142
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:08,420
 samopuzdanje mu se spušta,

1143
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:10,680
 sakriću drugi put ako i kako mogu,

1144
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:14,100
 znači jednostavno ne dobivamo ništa dobro.

1145
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:17,420
 Možda će paziti da drugi put ne napravi to isto,

1146
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:20,620
 da kao mu opet ne uzmeš mobiteli će napraviti nešto drugo.

1147
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:23,820
 Znači opet nisi gradio njegove vještine

1148
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:25,060
 koje mu trebaju za život.

1149
00:37:25,060 --> 00:37:28,320
 Znači mi u odgoju nismo tu da kažnjavamo

1150
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,520
 za ponašnje koje nije okej,

1151
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:32,420
 nego da gradimo vještine za ponašnje koje je okej.

1152
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:33,380
 Uf, daj prvi to.

1153
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,640
 Mislim, kužim što želiš reći,

1154
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:35,200
 ali ajde malo.

1155
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:39,680
 Baš zvuči kao da je cijelo bogatstvo u toj rečenici.

1156
00:37:40,020 --> 00:37:42,500
 I to je nekako ima osjećaj sve što sam do sad govorila.

1157
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:47,740
 To je da, znači, kad ja...

1158
00:37:47,740 --> 00:37:51,980
 Evo, koje alate, koji alati su onako primarni

1159
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:55,460
 za jedno djete koje će jednog dana,

1160
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:57,360
 pod tim mislim možda kad uđu pubertet,

1161
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,640
 te neke kritične, formativne godine,

1162
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:02,540
 će ti se moći obratiti s povjerenjem,

1163
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:03,960
 neće se skrivat, neće bježati.

1164
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:08,260
 Koje alate treba dati djetetu sad,

1165
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:10,000
 dok ima 3, 4, 5, 6 godina?

1166
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:12,020
 Razvijat emocijonalnu inteligenciju.

1167
00:38:12,020 --> 00:38:16,960
 A ona se razvija takvim pravilnim postavljanjem granica,

1168
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:18,780
 uključit će emocije.

1169
00:38:18,780 --> 00:38:21,020
 Znači da postavimo granicu ponašanju,

1170
00:38:21,020 --> 00:38:24,780
 imenujemo, aha, stvarno te zanimata čaša,

1171
00:38:24,780 --> 00:38:27,560
 ili baš si ljut na seku.

1172
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:30,020
 Znači, ako je on udario sestru,

1173
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:32,480
 bez toga baš si ljut na sestru,

1174
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,740
 da stvarno si ljut.

1175
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:36,040
 I razumijevanje, pa okej da bude ljut.

1176
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:38,120
 znači da dozvolimo emociju koju ima.

1177
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:40,260
 Jer kažnjavanjem ili stanjem u sobu,

1178
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:42,800
 mi smo izignorirali njegovu emociju koja je okej,

1179
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,420
 ljutnja je okej, ljutnja je borba za sebe.

1180
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:46,320
 Znači, stvarno si ljut.

1181
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:47,880
 Ne dozvoljavam da udaraš.

1182
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,800
 Što možeš napraviti kad si ljut?

1183
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:51,920
 I to je zapravo recept.

1184
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,480
 Znači, mama me vidi.

1185
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,980
 Mama mi ne da da to radim.

1186
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:57,700
 Mama je strogo rekla, to ne dozvoljavam.

1187
00:38:57,700 --> 00:38:59,720
 Vidim da si ljut.

1188
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:01,120
 Aha, okej, sad ja i razumijem,

1189
00:39:01,120 --> 00:39:02,780
 aha, pa da, udario sam sestru jer sam ljut.

1190
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:04,140
 Aha, okej, aha.

1191
00:39:04,140 --> 00:39:05,760
 Znači, to radim kad se ljutim, okej.

1192
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:07,660
 Ali mama mi ne da da to radi, znači to nije, okej.

1193
00:39:07,660 --> 00:39:08,760
 Okej.

1194
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:10,980
 I mama mi pokazuje što mogu.

1195
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:14,000
 Ali mama je, pošto me nije odbila i kaznila,

1196
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,300
 ona me već tim pristupom regulira.

1197
00:39:16,940 --> 00:39:22,600
 Jer dijete ne može, regulacija znači stavljanje svog tijela u smireno stanje.

1198
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:25,140
 Kožiš, znači osjećam se okej.

1199
00:39:25,140 --> 00:39:28,600
 I mama me već tim pristupom regulira

1200
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:34,020
 i kada tisuću milijon puta nadreguliramo svoje dijete,

1201
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:36,780
 ono onda razvije sposobnost regulacije samog sebe.

1202
00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:41,420
 I onda, znači, pokažemo dijete tu što može napraviti kad je ljuto.

1203
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:42,480
 Udariti ju ne smiješ.

1204
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:45,400
 Možeš joj reći ovako, stop, ne želim da mi to radiš.

1205
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:47,340
 Ili možeš joj reći, želim tu igračku.

1206
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:49,460
 Ili ako si jako ljut, možeš ovako stisnuti ruke.

1207
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:51,340
 Znači, dati mu primjere.

1208
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:54,560
 I zapravo, to je proces koji mi njega učimo.

1209
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:57,420
 Znači, narušavamo njegov integritet.

1210
00:39:57,420 --> 00:40:00,840
 Dakle, odgajamo jedno dijete koji ima pozitivnu sliku o sebi.

1211
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:03,800
 A takvi ljudi su bolji prema drugima.

1212
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:06,840
 Znači, ljudi koji rade drugima loše, ne osjećaju se dobro sami sa sobom.

1213
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:07,420
 Znači, to je prvo.

1214
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:10,800
 Drugo, razvija vještine emocijalne inteligencije.

1215
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:14,720
 Znači, svjesno sebi, svojim emocijama, emocijama i potrebama drugih.

1216
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:20,560
 Zato što, ako sam ja u tom procesu koji sam opisala, svjesna emocija i potreba njega,

1217
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:24,700
 on već modeliranjem uči kako se to radi.

1218
00:40:24,700 --> 00:40:30,400
 Onda će i on razumijet sutra više potrebe i emocije druge osobe.

1219
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:36,900
 Onda u tom procesu uči regulirat sebe i kontrolirat sebe.

1220
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,040
 Znači, zaustavit.

1221
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:41,400
 On mora prvo, dijete mora razumijet,

1222
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:46,020
 on mora znati, imenovati i osjetiti svoju emociju da bi mogo se kontrolirat.

1223
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:49,140
 Zato to oprosti što ovaj udara, nema smisla.

1224
00:40:49,140 --> 00:40:52,120
 Da god on ne nauči zašto udara,

1225
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:55,760
 aha, uzbuđen sam, on se neće moći kontrolirat.

1226
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:58,820
 Ok, osim ako ga udariš dobro, ali onda imaš posljedice neke druge.

1227
00:40:58,820 --> 00:40:59,900
 Tako, problem na problem.

1228
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:00,420
 Da, da, da.

1229
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:03,740
 Znači, bolje zamijeniti samo datnu alternativu, ajde kad si uzbuđen,

1230
00:41:03,740 --> 00:41:07,420
 jer ti dođu prijatelji i tako dalje, zagrli ih tipa ili tako nešto.

1231
00:41:07,420 --> 00:41:10,360
 Da, ali taj dio s emocijama mora biti,

1232
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,660
 to se zove empatiško reflektiranje.

1233
00:41:12,660 --> 00:41:15,000
 Primijetili si da sam rekla, uzbuđen si.

1234
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:18,340
 Ja moram živjeti emociju koju moje djete ima.

1235
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:20,380
 Kad je moje djete ljuto, da ljuci!

1236
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:23,560
 Znači, moj ton se prilagođava ljutnji.

1237
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:26,800
 Moj ton, moje lice, moje tijelo,

1238
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:29,940
 jer ono tako uči o svojim emocijama i o sebi.

1239
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:32,500
 I tako uči prepoznat emocije drugih.

1240
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:35,860
 I vidi da, aha, ok, to sad moji sestri sve to ok,

1241
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:37,960
 znači, ovo mogla bi biti užena ljuta trara.

1242
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:42,060
 Znači, zapravo ga mi opismenjavamo da je on u odnosima ok.

1243
00:41:42,060 --> 00:41:43,960
 I da su sve emocije ok.

1244
00:41:44,160 --> 00:41:45,360
 Znači, samo ne sve radnje.

1245
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:48,140
 Tako da, to je sav taj proces koji sad izgleda složan.

1246
00:41:48,140 --> 00:41:50,740
 Ono, kroz edukaciju, stvarno idemo korak po korak

1247
00:41:50,740 --> 00:41:52,160
 i slažu se te kocke.

1248
00:41:52,160 --> 00:41:53,820
 Ali to je to što sam ima bitla,

1249
00:41:53,820 --> 00:41:56,400
 to je proces kojim naše djete onda postaje

1250
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,560
 zrelije,

1251
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:59,620
 odgovornije,

1252
00:41:59,620 --> 00:42:01,300
 bolje prema drugima,

1253
00:42:01,300 --> 00:42:03,060
 poštuje više tebe,

1254
00:42:03,060 --> 00:42:05,100
 empatičnije

1255
00:42:05,100 --> 00:42:07,480
 i to što sam rekla

1256
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,360
 dokazano je da djece koji imaju višu emocijonalni,

1257
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:11,600
 da je emocijna inteligencija već je

1258
00:42:11,600 --> 00:42:14,440
 prediktor uspjeha od logičke,

1259
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:15,880
 odnosno od IQ-a,

1260
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,960
 od kvazijenta inteligencije.

1261
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:20,020
 A ono što, na što se mi svi

1262
00:42:20,020 --> 00:42:21,620
 usmjeravamo je samo to da je

1263
00:42:21,620 --> 00:42:23,060
 inteligentno, znanje,

1264
00:42:23,060 --> 00:42:24,640
 ok, ali

1265
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:27,920
 najveći prediktor uspjeha je emocijonalna inteligencija

1266
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:30,540
 i čak utječe i na fizičko zdravlje,

1267
00:42:30,540 --> 00:42:32,200
 na sreću u životu,

1268
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:33,800
 na akademski uspjeh,

1269
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:36,480
 na karijeru,

1270
00:42:36,480 --> 00:42:38,100
 znači ono, koliko je to važno.

1271
00:42:38,100 --> 00:42:40,200
 Znači moramo se time baviti u odgoju.

1272
00:42:40,200 --> 00:42:40,760
 Da.

1273
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:43,800
 Ali evo, počeli smo se baviti time više.

1274
00:42:43,800 --> 00:42:44,460
 Baš sam htjela reći,

1275
00:42:44,460 --> 00:42:45,100
 apropo ovog,

1276
00:42:45,100 --> 00:42:47,280
 kad smo komentirali prethodne generacije,

1277
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:49,820
 opet moram malo,

1278
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:51,620
 malo im dati,

1279
00:42:51,620 --> 00:42:52,940
 kako se to uopće na hrvatskom kaže,

1280
00:42:53,020 --> 00:42:56,340
 milosti i prema tim starijim generacijama,

1281
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,840
 to su opet neke generacije

1282
00:42:57,840 --> 00:43:00,460
 koje nisu nekako nimale vremena

1283
00:43:00,460 --> 00:43:01,620
 baviti se time,

1284
00:43:01,620 --> 00:43:05,400
 jer su vrlo često više brnuli za egzistenciju.

1285
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:07,520
 Ja, moćemo mi sad u ovoj blagodati,

1286
00:43:07,520 --> 00:43:09,720
 možemo se više posjetiti tome.

1287
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:11,200
 Onda se opet nekad pitam,

1288
00:43:11,200 --> 00:43:13,680
 možda sad idem previše u filozofiju,

1289
00:43:13,680 --> 00:43:16,740
 ali je li onda ova današnja metoda,

1290
00:43:16,740 --> 00:43:17,920
 svjesno roditeljstvo,

1291
00:43:17,920 --> 00:43:20,240
 samo kritika na tradicionalni odgoj?

1292
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:22,340
 I što onda dolazi nakon toga?

1293
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:26,380
 Što će biti kritika na svjesno roditeljstvo?

1294
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:30,000
 Odnosno, kakve krive drine će ispravljati naša djeca?

1295
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,500
 Na svoje djece?

1296
00:43:31,500 --> 00:43:34,660
 Pa mislim da će biti taj dio popustljivosti,

1297
00:43:34,660 --> 00:43:36,600
 ako svjesno odlazi u popustljivo,

1298
00:43:36,600 --> 00:43:39,180
 da se ne zna da je ipak roditelj taj koji vodi.

1299
00:43:39,180 --> 00:43:45,080
 Jer je tanka granica između popustljivog

1300
00:43:45,080 --> 00:43:47,540
 i roditeljstva gdje postoje jasne i čvrste granice

1301
00:43:47,540 --> 00:43:48,680
 i jasna očekivanja.

1302
00:43:48,680 --> 00:43:50,620
 Jer danas, ne znam,

1303
00:43:50,620 --> 00:43:52,380
 ti sjedeš na tu stolicu,

1304
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:53,680
 djete želi, oni se dižu.

1305
00:43:53,680 --> 00:43:56,540
 Znači, jer eto, on želi baš tajtenjur,

1306
00:43:56,540 --> 00:43:58,240
 baš tu stolicu, baš ovo, baš ono,

1307
00:43:58,240 --> 00:43:59,800
 okej, želiš?

1308
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:01,100
 I ja sam sjela.

1309
00:44:01,100 --> 00:44:03,600
 Znači, u redu je nekad,

1310
00:44:03,600 --> 00:44:04,840
 evo, baš djete želi.

1311
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:07,760
 Ali ono, ne mora sve biti kako djete želi.

1312
00:44:07,900 --> 00:44:09,140
 Ili ja uvijek dam jedan primjer

1313
00:44:09,140 --> 00:44:12,520
 u kojem sam osvjesla, jer vidim druge roditelje

1314
00:44:12,520 --> 00:44:15,800
 koji se trude biti svjesni i sebe.

1315
00:44:15,800 --> 00:44:18,300
 E sad primjer, bili smo kod prijateljice u dvorištu

1316
00:44:18,300 --> 00:44:19,260
 i mi jedemo ručak.

1317
00:44:19,260 --> 00:44:21,140
 I moja kćer je naravno pojela,

1318
00:44:21,140 --> 00:44:22,280
 promrljala, okej,

1319
00:44:22,280 --> 00:44:24,060
 znači pojela je koliko je htjela

1320
00:44:24,060 --> 00:44:25,660
 i otišla je na ljuljačku.

1321
00:44:25,660 --> 00:44:28,140
 I ja jedem, mama ljuljaj me, mama ljuljaj me.

1322
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:30,080
 Ja se nisam dignula, ja jedem.

1323
00:44:30,080 --> 00:44:32,280
 To je moja osobna granica.

1324
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:34,100
 Ja trenutno jedem, ljubavi vidim,

1325
00:44:34,100 --> 00:44:35,660
 jako biš voljala da te ljuljam.

1326
00:44:35,660 --> 00:44:37,580
 Kad pojedem, ću doć.

1327
00:44:37,580 --> 00:44:39,740
 Većina roditelja, odmah,

1328
00:44:39,740 --> 00:44:41,440
 jer oni moraju biti prisutni roditelji

1329
00:44:41,440 --> 00:44:43,460
 koji što god djete zamisli,

1330
00:44:43,460 --> 00:44:44,180
 tu sam ja.

1331
00:44:44,180 --> 00:44:47,360
 Mislim, ili to ne znam,

1332
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,180
 ne znam ni koliko je povezno,

1333
00:44:49,180 --> 00:44:49,960
 ali došlo mi je na um,

1334
00:44:49,960 --> 00:44:51,980
 pa ću reći da roditelji djece,

1335
00:44:52,120 --> 00:44:54,300
 prijateljica mi ide, djevojčica njena

1336
00:44:54,300 --> 00:44:54,980
 u prvi razred.

1337
00:44:54,980 --> 00:44:57,960
 Kad dobio peticu, odmah idu kupi darove.

1338
00:44:57,960 --> 00:45:00,300
 Molim, ono, darove,

1339
00:45:00,300 --> 00:45:02,060
 jer si dobila pet.

1340
00:45:02,060 --> 00:45:04,440
 Znači, ono, ajmo predstav

1341
00:45:04,440 --> 00:45:06,420
 da su nam se ponašati

1342
00:45:06,420 --> 00:45:07,640
 kao da su nam djeca projekt.

1343
00:45:07,640 --> 00:45:10,600
 Znači, pusti ga da ono uči radi sebe,

1344
00:45:10,600 --> 00:45:12,880
 a ne da uči da bi dobilo dar.

1345
00:45:12,880 --> 00:45:14,920
 Znači, mislim da je u današnjem svijetu

1346
00:45:14,920 --> 00:45:18,580
 udoljavanje od tog unutarnjeg

1347
00:45:18,580 --> 00:45:19,760
 vlastitog vrednovanja,

1348
00:45:19,760 --> 00:45:21,680
 unutarnjeg lokusa kontrola.

1349
00:45:21,740 --> 00:45:23,660
 Ako ti kupuješ dar, ti si kontrola.

1350
00:45:23,660 --> 00:45:26,220
 I ne želim ja bi, ja učim svoje djete

1351
00:45:26,220 --> 00:45:28,440
 da ono kontrolira sebe,

1352
00:45:28,440 --> 00:45:29,360
 da ono vodi sebe.

1353
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,540
 Ja tu jesam vođa, da,

1354
00:45:30,540 --> 00:45:33,020
 ali ne da ću ga, ono,

1355
00:45:33,020 --> 00:45:35,180
 popuštat mu, kupovat mu nešto.

1356
00:45:35,180 --> 00:45:36,700
 Znači, ono, ajmo ga pustiti

1357
00:45:36,700 --> 00:45:37,740
 da bude odgovorno

1358
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:39,960
 i da može vrednovat samo sebe,

1359
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:41,420
 a ne da ono gleda mene ko Boga

1360
00:45:41,420 --> 00:45:43,340
 i ono mora učit za pede

1361
00:45:43,340 --> 00:45:44,560
 da bi dobilo dar

1362
00:45:44,560 --> 00:45:45,880
 ili da ja ne bi vikala,

1363
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:48,400
 ono, ne, unutarnju motivaciju

1364
00:45:48,400 --> 00:45:49,940
 trebamo poticati.

1365
00:45:49,940 --> 00:45:51,120
 To zvuči

1366
00:45:51,120 --> 00:45:53,600
 kao jedan, onako,

1367
00:45:53,600 --> 00:45:54,600
 idealni cilj

1368
00:45:54,600 --> 00:45:55,700
 koji svimi roditelji želimo

1369
00:45:55,700 --> 00:45:56,920
 dostići,

1370
00:45:56,920 --> 00:45:57,960
 da mi je djete, ono,

1371
00:45:57,960 --> 00:45:59,900
 samo pouzdano,

1372
00:45:59,900 --> 00:46:02,340
 da ima to izgrađeno čvrsto,

1373
00:46:02,340 --> 00:46:02,700
 ja,

1374
00:46:02,700 --> 00:46:04,500
 evo, baš ću se sad

1375
00:46:04,500 --> 00:46:05,920
 osunuti na jedno od pitanja,

1376
00:46:05,920 --> 00:46:07,620
 makar se radi o malo starijem djetetu,

1377
00:46:07,620 --> 00:46:08,540
 mama je napisala,

1378
00:46:08,540 --> 00:46:09,600
 evo, pročitacu,

1379
00:46:10,660 --> 00:46:13,280
 Han, valjda je povezano,

1380
00:46:13,280 --> 00:46:13,840
 mislim da je.

1381
00:46:13,840 --> 00:46:14,640
 Vidjet će.

1382
00:46:14,640 --> 00:46:16,260
 Kako se postaviti,

1383
00:46:16,260 --> 00:46:17,140
 što reći curici

1384
00:46:17,140 --> 00:46:18,920
 svojeg čeri,

1385
00:46:18,920 --> 00:46:19,100
 ali,

1386
00:46:19,100 --> 00:46:21,800
 u ulazku u pubertet,

1387
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:23,060
 kad ju najbolja prijateljica

1388
00:46:23,060 --> 00:46:24,300
 od rođenja

1389
00:46:24,300 --> 00:46:25,140
 ignorira

1390
00:46:25,140 --> 00:46:26,840
 kad god dođe nekad treća.

1391
00:46:26,840 --> 00:46:28,120
 Očito je ljubomora,

1392
00:46:28,120 --> 00:46:28,960
 te prijateljice

1393
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:30,040
 na određene uspjehe

1394
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:30,640
 prisutna,

1395
00:46:30,640 --> 00:46:31,780
 ali uporno

1396
00:46:31,780 --> 00:46:33,300
 povređuje svoju prijateljicu,

1397
00:46:33,300 --> 00:46:34,520
 bilo o malovažavanjem,

1398
00:46:34,520 --> 00:46:35,640
 glumatanjem,

1399
00:46:35,640 --> 00:46:36,680
 uzdizanjem sebe,

1400
00:46:36,680 --> 00:46:37,520
 što savjetovati,

1401
00:46:37,520 --> 00:46:38,980
 inače smo i kućni prijatelji,

1402
00:46:40,660 --> 00:46:41,160
 roditeljima,

1403
00:46:41,160 --> 00:46:43,080
 ili kako pristupiti,

1404
00:46:43,080 --> 00:46:43,800
 već je par puta,

1405
00:46:43,800 --> 00:46:44,100
 kaže,

1406
00:46:44,100 --> 00:46:46,160
 plakala u takvim situacijama.

1407
00:46:46,160 --> 00:46:47,740
 Kako napravi to

1408
00:46:47,740 --> 00:46:49,260
 da ti djete dovoljno opet čvrsto,

1409
00:46:49,260 --> 00:46:50,160
 da ga kao ne diraju

1410
00:46:50,160 --> 00:46:51,060
 te vanjske stvari,

1411
00:46:51,060 --> 00:46:52,620
 jel to ima veze s tim

1412
